Ole Dammegard interviews Robyn of How I See The World YouTube channel, discussing his work uncovering the deception behind staged events such as the Orlando Pulse Gay Night Club Shooting Hoax and many many more.

His speciality is to make direct calls to crisis actors, hospitals, FBI and authorities, asking direct and very revealing questions.
